name: Bill Ready
tweet: The potential to work together to revamp the infrastructure & increase access to the digital economy has never been greater. Over the past 2+ years, @PayPal has forged 40+ partnerships. Together, we can build & democratize access seamless commerce experiences. #Money2020

name: Bill Ready
tweet: Businesses of all sizes should have access to the tools that let them thrive in their local & broader communities. They can do that if we come together & create solutions that increase access and level the playing field for businesses of all sizes. #Money2020

name: Bill Ready
tweet: Today’s financial infrastructure wasn’t designed for small biz. >50% of small biz are locked in the physical world yet 48% of consumers would consider not buying from a biz if it didn’t have a website. Small biz are missing out on opportunities to reach customers. #Money2020

name: Bill Ready
tweet: Although technology has made getting access to global customers faster, it’s made getting access to money slower for businesses. Technology should make it easier to get your money, not harder. @PayPal is working to solve this with solutions like Funds Now. #Money2020

name: Bill Ready
tweet: The digital economy has created tremendous opportunities, but the benefits of digitization haven’t been evenly distributed. You see this everyday with retailers going bankrupt & storefronts closing. What’s less visible is small businesses are hurting just as badly. #Money2020

name: Bill Ready
tweet: Small businesses are the backbone of our economy. There are ~30M small businesses in the US & many tens of millions more globally. Those small businesses account for over 60% of job growth & are truly the engine of our economy. #Money2020 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zXBYxq0qIxg …
